650
01:06:09,800 --> 01:06:11,940
You know how new blankets are all crinkly.

651
01:06:11,940 --> 01:06:13,210
And they feel nice.

652
01:06:13,610 --> 01:06:15,210
I fell right asleep.

653
01:06:18,350 --> 01:06:19,780
- The blanket. - I'm positive.

654
01:06:22,820 --> 01:06:24,220
