01:07:19,470 --> 01:07:20,940
You see what?

663
01:07:23,840 --> 01:07:25,310
Why are you so awkward?

664
01:07:32,450 --> 01:07:33,690
When I was coming here...

665
01:07:35,060 --> 01:07:36,560
It's not like we made plans,

666
01:07:38,630 --> 01:07:39,690
but I hoped...

667
01:07:40,860 --> 01:07:42,200
